        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A patchwork of humanoid flesh makes up this grotesque mask stitched together with black silk or wire. It is distinctive for its bulbous orange eye- crafted from a magical glass bauble-and wide row of teeth.</p>\n<p>When worn, the mask amplifies your ability to sense fear in other creatures.</p>\n<p>You automatically know the value of the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened} condition of any @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Observed]{Observed} creature, and you gain a +1 item bonus to Perception checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Seek]{Seek} frightened creatures. Whenever you deal precision damage to a frightened creature, you deal 1 additional precision damage.</p>\n<p>If you are not evil, you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained} 2 while wearing the<em>Skinsaw mask</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+1 item bonus to Perception checks to Seek frightened creatures</li>\n</ul>"
